{"tid":1526743,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"示威者衝擊機場保安防線","createTime":"2019-09-01T07:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T07:20:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e16776337c9ddd08c715fc0edd14ee7ebab488e","tid":1526743,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:15:18.000Z","msg":"示威者衝擊機場保安防線<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n <br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n  今日（九月一日）下午一時開始，大批示威者聚集機場客運大樓巴士站一帶。至下午兩時許，示威者開始衝擊水馬，以鐳射光線射向機場管理局（機管局）職員，又用行李車和鐵欄堵路，更向警員及機管局職員投擲雜物。有關示威者正參與未經批准的集結。<br />\n   <br />\n  由於機場的法庭禁制令仍然生效，示威者的行為有機會構成藐視法庭。警方警告示威者立即停止違法行為及離開。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年9月1日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間14時38分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/01/P2019090100516.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201909%2F01%2FP2019090100516.htm&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=f5e57438\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/01/P2019090100516.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a2f08a180e663aeb602dbac3335019a721306a65","tid":1526743,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e55e60736398774100e50b28804e62a87948830","tid":1526743,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJt14fQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJt14fQ.jpg&h=a06522ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68b39aa52df3b69127cb2c946dab615942307a58","tid":1526743,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:19:44.000Z","msg":"又黎教傳媒做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df0da1e1eb30ee38fc4353e279f8af098e674de","tid":1526743,"uid":248588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e55e60736398774100e50b28804e62a87948830","tid":1526743,"uid"